      • DEFAULT_PIN_RULES

        public static final java.util.List<PinRule> DEFAULT_PIN_RULES
        Default PIN rules for changePin operation. It contains All of rules as follow:
        • PinRuleIdentical
        • PinRuleUniform
        • PinRulePalindrome
        • PinRuleSeries
        • PinRuleLength
